    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All of God’s riches compressed into this seed,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Equally precious faith, will meet our need;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s divine energy, virtue from within,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Supplies the way to make us just like Him."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Virtue brings knowledge of our Lord Jesus Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s divine power, and Christ to be our life;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And, with all diligence, His life we will absorb,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "While rooted, grounded in God’s Holy Word."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Richly and bountif’lly supplied unto you,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is an entrance to the kingdom in view;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let us be diligent to enter in,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We grow, develop, enter into Him!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Self-control, dwells in the structure of the tree,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Self kept in check, from our spirit is set free;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life now can flow and our passions and our lust"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Will be restrained, for this in God we trust."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ our endurance will branch, increase, and grow;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Passing though hardship, Christ’s sufferings we know;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our daily living with spirit exercised,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Expresses God to be our kingdom prize."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
